{"questionId":"68b576c1-9de8-41d3-9840-538d4edcd113_14","correctAnswer":"D","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Set up","content":"Substitute $x = 4$ into each function: $f(4) = 4 + 5 = 9$ and $g(4) = 5(4) = 20$."},{"title":"Solve","content":"$$7f(4) - g(4) = 7(9) - 20 = 63 - 20 = 43$$"},{"title":"Answer","content":"<strong>D</strong> is correct."}]}